{"id": "1247595883013341356", "channel_id": "1247463554802520065", "type": 19, "author_id": "1002938431271358494", "author_name": "1027vliaji", "author_bot": false, "content": "高练度神父应该可以，神父觉醒有屏障，道中有2费的群攻，应该可以替换艾继丝，但是BOSS战的时候，如果算力造物不够，不能每回合开出一次钥令，环娜的【命定之剑】，伤害可能会差一些。", "timestamp": "2024-06-04T17:00:37.721000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1122207553053528217"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1247585978822955091", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1247463554802520065", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "癫狂五3W分，血肉环娜攻略", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1243105047332524043", "1174179734373019748"]}
