{"id": "1247375359326818314", "channel_id": "1247375359326818314", "type": 0, "author_id": "1073914607741177866", "author_name": "scholar_2", "author_bot": false, "content": "1-4：沒什麽好説的，水母攢到7回合秒了，6回合boss剛好不輸出，切換靜海上盾7回合轉爆發就行，戈利亞爽吸力量\n2-4：雖然我打的是新boss，但依舊可以用希洛隊，舊版造物+2算和送打擊更加適配，問題在於打舊版boss需要提前儸坦清屏障以及注意小怪的封印\n3-4：不管是24還是魔術師都是尤烏特攻環節，問題不是很大，區別在於魔術師的多段沒那麽好防守\n4-4：最討厭的一集，1和5一把過，2和3兩把過，4打了三把凹了無數次才過，混沌隊的生存屬實拉跨（也可能因爲我諾沒練，沒法用，女仆換諾或許會好打很多，也可以用艾特攻boss塞卡\n5-4：練度足夠的話依舊推薦水母+戈利亞，純純的特攻。用血肉打的時候需要注意，boss有一個單體和群體的連著兩回合攻擊，前者會根據印記上減力量，後者會吃印記給力量，石化建議用在高攻減完力量的那回合，這樣把減力量拖過去，下回合可以對軸輸出", "timestamp": "2024-06-04T02:24:20.777000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 7}], "attachments": [{"id": "1247375359670747146", "filename": "0733SV94QESSLBYOE.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 245366, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1247375359326818314/1247375359670747146/0733SV94QESSLBYOE.png?ex=69cbd914&is=69ca8794&hm=9aa9971cc05af1b0a692acfd44aa1c64b90e6e039068d1a7fe1e424d3533908f&"}, {"id": "1247375360039977097", "filename": "LVEDU4O8DRZAC9SU.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 617258, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1247375359326818314/1247375360039977097/LVEDU4O8DRZAC9SU.png?ex=69cbd914&is=69ca8794&hm=ad9f6de98e9ae91f58e14f09942458c0b95bd64d70a17ada6f2362d8cd4bac7f&"}, {"id": "1247375360350228511", "filename": "NL273Z2L1L1JKZZNR.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 602960, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1247375359326818314/1247375360350228511/NL273Z2L1L1JKZZNR.png?ex=69cbd915&is=69ca8795&hm=66a703de5b72e0f7d3dbbc6232824e99eaba2fb1ff32d6197cfbebd6c31071b4&"}, {"id": "1247375360685768704", "filename": "MNGXYG85R74M7402IDC.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 646691, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1247375359326818314/1247375360685768704/MNGXYG85R74M7402IDC.png?ex=69cbd915&is=69ca8795&hm=34d0f7fb2c5c86cde39b500d983a19c6be5dd38b321e726dc